{
  "texts": [
    "Instead of a traditional fully connected approach, we separate the input data into ten smaller chunks, each comprising 32 units.",
    "Each of these chunks is processed through a specific module, consisting of a linear layer with 32 input features and 3 output features.",
    "The collective output from these ten modules produces the final prediction.",
    "Nature Communications | (2024) 15:129"
  ]
}